    There are two kinds of service types in Leonardo ML Foundation on Cloud Foundry: The Cloud Foundry Leonardo ML service type and the Leonardo ML Foundation service type. Leonardo ML Foundation doesn't supply each of its services as individual Cloud Foundry services, but one Cloud Foundry service wrapping all Leonardo ML Services with their URLs listed in the credentials part of the Cloud Foundry service.

    This type indicates the Cloud Foundry service type to use.

    See the 'Environment Variables' section in an application with a Leonardo ML Service binding to see the raw information.
